org.opendaylight.controller.protocol_plugin.openflow.vendorextension.v6extension

Class V6StatsReply

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openflow.protocol.statistics.OFVendorStatistics
      • org.opendaylight.controller.protocol_plugin.openflow.vendorextension.v6extension.V6StatsReply
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, org.openflow.protocol.factory.OFActionFactoryAware, org.openflow.protocol.statistics.OFStatistics

    public class V6StatsReply
extends org.openflow.protocol.statistics.OFVendorStatistics
    This Class processes the OpenFlow Vendor Extension Reply message of a Stats Request. It parses the reply message and initializes fields of V6StatsReply object. Multiple instances of this class objects are created and used by OpenDaylight's Troubleshooting Application.
